title: Flash2X Screensaver Builder v3.0.0 WinALL-BRD
description: Flash2X Screensaver Builder is a program to create flash screensavers with both flash (SWF) and flash videos (FLV). It generates executable installers to help you distribute your flash screensavers. You are allowed to customize the flash screensavers with your logo and your business information. It is a great piece of software for both personal use and business promotion.
